An '''unidentified Underworld species''' dwelled in the sewers of the [[Coruscant Underworld/Legends|Coruscant underworld]] around [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]]. They were a small, winged [[Species/Legends|species]] with [[Color/Legends|green]] fangs, which lived in the ruins of ancient buildings. They revered [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] for unknown reasons.

It was customary of the species to exchange gifts upon meeting new people. When [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] and his entourage encountered the Underworld avians circa [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]], they swapped weapons for [[glowworm]]s to assure the creatures they harbored no ill will towards them.

